snippet.title: Espresso Tycoon - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
📣 From now on you can add the Espresso Tycoon game to your Steam wishlist!
▶️ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1543280/Espresso_Tycoon/ 

Jump into a world full of picky customers, intriguing opportunities, and delicious coffee! Test your management skills and build a successful coffee business!
